Gymnastics Leotard Set
(College of Winterhold Gymnastics Club, Skyrim, Japan, Romania)
descriptionHtml:
Name:Gymnastics Leotard -CBBE
Version: 1.0
Date: 2013/07/14
by Shimaneko
-------------------[ Description ]-----------------------
This mod adds to the game gymnastics leotards for CBBE body.
The base body was made by \"BodySlide.exe\".
It supports the weight slider.
These are registered as Light Armor.

How to get: 
Uses leather and garnet at the forge.
It upgrades using a diamond. 

ItemID:
Leotard Skyrim (Black)      XX001D98
Leotard Skyrim (Purple)     XX001D99
Leotard Winterhold (Green)  XX001D9A
Leotard Winterhold (Pink)   XX001D9B
Leotard Japan (Black)       XX001D9C
Leotard Japan (White)       XX001D9D
Leotard Romania (White)     XX001D9E
Leotard Romania (Blue)      XX001D9F

Garnet   00063b45
Diamond  00063b47 

If you like the mod, please upload your screens!
